Package: summary.target
Title: Summarize a Target Numeric Variable in a Data Frame by Specified Grouping Variables
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Zhili", "Jiang", email = "zhili.jiang@stat.ubc.ca", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides a convenient function for computing summary statistics, including mean,
  minimum, maximum, and standard deviation, on a specified numeric column in a data frame, 
  grouped by selected categorical variables. 
  This package aims to simplify grouped data analysis for users working with tidy data.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
